(144, 13, '2017-04-27 22:38:04', '2017-04-28 02:38:04', 'The other day I had a weird dream, as I do quite often. This one involved the club taking a trip to an amusement park for Patsy\'s birthday I think who really knows, but while there Luanne and I were heading to the bathroom when we saw a news alert on a TV. There was a car crash and one of the victims was BRIGGS. It didn\'t say whether he was alive or not and then the dream ended. After that I didn\'t see Briggs for like two days and lowkey thought he was actually in some sort of accident. Glad you\'re okay Briggs!\r\nSorry for any inappropriately structured sentences in this blog post, Katrina, but we should take what we can get considering nothings been posted here in over a month.', 'RIP Briggs??', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'rip-briggs', '', '', '2017-04-27 22:38:04', '2017-04-28 02:38:04', '', 0, 'http://umdclubrunning.com/blog/?p=144', 0, 'post', '', 2),
