tle bit over the summer.</em> Check out my tweet from May 15, 2016 at 3:07 am for evidence. End season 2/8.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/2ibxls3ewEJnh3N6FAkEX0TUBBhSaN9j0Kk4eR0DJh694G5oR9ipXpNztuzqYg4Y4-73nfb5bcxwobPhCSZNWkbvDEsCP9Y2DB3r98idaGUCgiEg5KVo7iUUpCiRZwtsqQsFHVhH\" alt=\"\" /><figcaption><em>:)</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/xBNFdDsc8FXOHuN0HkdgHSje-LFhTemJdt71RGtxsmbyo3QasQ24UwO-Lc2V0hSsTTYcS9wSf5kOL8H1JUUCGZTOHk6V2v0nQTK6Vj2-dF-aPgOUSTYPjnadbHafRbNj08mAwECL\" alt=\"\" /><figcaption><em>Group shot from the Frederick Half</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'My Journey Through Club Running: Part 2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '407-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-11-09 23:31:20', '2019-11-10 04:31:20', '', 407, 'http://umdclubrunning.com/blog/407-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
